Takeshi, it's been so long.
You've grown so much.

511
00:38:05,188 --> 00:38:06,022
Mrs. Toki?!

512
00:38:06,022 --> 00:38:06,690
This way!
Mrs. Toki?!

513
00:38:06,690 --> 00:38:07,486
This way!

514
00:38:09,259 --> 00:38:13,286
But I thought you and my father
were enemies?

515
