How can I explain this?

516
00:38:20,403 --> 00:38:22,769
There's all kinds of friendship.

517
00:38:25,575 --> 00:38:28,100
Takeshi, a cup of tea?

518
00:38:28,645 --> 00:38:30,772
No, thank you. I'm in a bit of a hurry.

519
00:38:34,684 --> 00:38:39,422
Mr. And Mrs. Toki, see you later.

520
00:38:39,422 --> 00:38:41,151
Wait, Takeshi!

521
00:38:42,259 --> 00:38:43,988
Well, since it's all prepared, would
you like a cup of tea, Honey?

522
00:38:44,261 --> 00:38:46,092
Sure...

