548
00:41:02,699 --> 00:41:04,166
Granny!

549
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:19,444
Watch out, Granny! Granny!

550
00:41:30,093 --> 00:41:34,325
Grandma... Grandma, I'd like you to
keep this for me.

551
00:41:34,764 --> 00:41:38,401
Grandpa, but it's the Toki family
heirloom sword.

552
00:41:38,401 --> 00:41:40,301
The most important thing next to your
life. I can't.

553
00:41:41,204 --> 00:41:44,503
I can't take it with me to heaven.

554
00:41:46,042 --> 00:41:47,976
What's wrong, Grandma?

555
00:41:48,812 --> 00:41:57,914
It's the first time you've ever given
me anything.

556
00:42:16,339 --> 00:42:17,897
