559
00:42:29,919 --> 00:42:32,217
Okay, okay, okay.

560
00:42:32,722 --> 00:42:34,189
Slowly, slowly.

561
00:42:38,394 --> 00:42:40,123
Carry them out carefully. Careful!

562
00:42:41,064 --> 00:42:42,964
They're hard as rock.

563
00:42:43,299 --> 00:42:45,699
Hey, there's one more here!

564
00:42:49,105 --> 00:42:51,835
Good job! Please have some!

565
00:42:59,816 --> 00:43:01,374
Aren't you glad we came, Ayako?

566
00:43:04,020 --> 00:43:05,487
Here you go!

567
00:43:14,063 --> 00:43:15,655
